---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import HeroImage from '../../components/HeroImage.astro';
import analysisHero from '../../assets/images/heroes/analysis-index.jpg';
---

<Base
  title="Ghana Business Analysis: Economic Reports, Sector Intelligence, Risk Assessments"
  description="In-depth Ghana business analysis for investors and diaspora founders. Sector rankings, risk alerts, policy tracking, and opportunity scoring. Updated continuously."
  keywords="Ghana economic analysis, Ghana business report, Ghana investment analysis, Ghana sector report 2026, Ghana risk assessment, diaspora investment guide"
>
  <HeroImage
    image={analysisHero}
    alt="Ghana commerce and trade, the foundation of economic analysis"
    credit="Julie Blake Edison"
    creditSource="Unsplash"
    height={380}
  >
    <h1 style="font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Ghana Business Analysis</h1>
    <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);max-width:600px;">Evidence-grounded analysis powered by GhanaWorld v3.0. 25 agents, real-time web research, no hype.</p>
  </HeroImage>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Published Reports</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <a href="/analysis/hormuz-crisis-ghana-2026" class="card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit">
        <span class="card-tag risk">Risk Alert</span>
        <h3>Hormuz Crisis: How $114 Oil Reaches a Ghanaian Market Stall</h3>
        <p>Diesel up 25.7% in one NPA window. Four transmission channels traced with real pricing data. Sector-by-sector impact. What to watch next.</p>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span>March 28, 2026</span>
          <span>Macro and Global</span>
          <span>12 min read</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="section-header" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
      <h2>In the Pipeline</h2>
      <p>Articles advancing through the 8-stage publishing pipeline with 3 mandatory quality gates.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card" style="opacity:0.7">
        <span class="card-tag risk">Risk Alert</span>
        <h3>GSE Crash: 73% Rally to 18% Weekly Drop</h3>
        <p>Historic highs to sharp correction. Is 12,990 the floor or a waypoint? Volume analysis and scenario modeling.</p>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span>Stage 4</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="opacity:0.7">
        <span class="card-tag policy">Policy Analysis</span>
        <h3>BoG Rate Cut to 14%: What the Split Vote Means</h3>
        <p>The 3-1-1 vote reveals the tension between easing and Hormuz risk. May MPC is the critical decision point.</p>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span>Stage 1</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="opacity:0.7">
        <span class="card-tag">Scenario Analysis</span>
        <h3>Ghana's Triple Shock: Three Scenarios for 2026</h3>
        <p>Hormuz, cocoa, and GSE hit simultaneously. Base case, upside, downside, and wildcard with probability estimates.</p>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span>Stage 1</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
